      "text": "This is a win for law and order. After days of @GovSherrillNJ REFUSING to allow State Police to assist @ICEgov law enforcement against violent anti-ICE rioters, she is now allowing the New Jersey State Police to cooperate with us. Thank you, Governor.\n\nAssaulting and obstructing ICE law enforcement is a crime and felony. Anyone who assaults federal law enforcement will be prosecuted to the fullest extent of the law. This violence against law enforcement must end.",
